         <div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">

<ab><lb n="1"/><persName key="FlZeno" type="attested"><name nymRef="#Φλάβιος"><expan><abbr>Φλ</abbr><ex>άβιος</ex></expan></name> <name nymRef="#Ζήνων">Ζήνων</name></persName> <rs type="official-relig" key="highpriest"><w lemma="ἀρχιερεύς">ἀρχιερεὺς</w></rs> <w lemma="καί">καὶ</w><lb n="2"/><rs type="dignity" key="comes"><w lemma="κόμης">κόμης</w></rs> <w lemma="ποιέω">ἐποίει</w> <w lemma="καί">καὶ</w> <w lemma="ὁ">τῇ</w> <w lemma="ἑαυτός">ἑαυ<lb n="3" break="no"/>τοῦ</w> <w lemma="πατρίς">πατρίδι</w> <w lemma="προῖκα">προῖκα</w> <w lemma="κατά">κα<lb n="4" break="no"/>τὰ</w> <w lemma="διαθήκη">διαθήκας</w> <w lemma="διά">διὰ</w> <w lemma="ὁ">τῶν</w> <w lemma="ἑαυτός"><expan><abbr>ἑαυτ</abbr><ex>οῦ</ex></expan></w><lb n="5"/><w lemma="παῖς">παίδων</w> <w lemma="ἀνατίθημι">ἀνέθηκεν</w> <g ref="#leaf"/>
</ab>
</div>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>
Fl<supplied reason="abbreviation">avius</supplied> Zenon, high priest and <foreign xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" xsl:lang="la">comes</foreign>, made this and set it up for his own homeland at his own expense, according to <supplied reason="subaudible">the terms of</supplied> his will <supplied reason="subaudible">carried out</supplied> by his own children.</ab>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>
For Flavius Zenon see also <ref type="inscription" n="11" target="050301.xml"/>, and discussion at <ref type="eAla-text" n="II.25" target=".xml"/>.</p>
         </div>
